			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Ngemini yesithoba kwasondeza inkulu yoonyana bakaBhenjamin, uAbhidan unyana kaGidiyoni.",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Umsondezo wakhe waba sisitya esinye sesilivere, bulikhulu elinamanci mathathu eeshekele ubunzima baso; sasinye isitya sokutshiza sesilivere, esiziishekele ezimashumi asixhenxe ngokweshekele yengcwele, zozibini zizele ngumgubo ocoliweyo womnikelo wokudla, ugalelwe ioli;",
