			"66": "<sup>66</sup> Ngemini yeshumi kwasondeza inkulu yoonyana bakaDan, uAhiyezere, unyana ka-Amishadayi.",
			"67": "<sup>67</sup> Umsondezo wakhe waba sisitya esinye sesilivere, bulikhulu elinamanci mathathu eeshekele ubunzima baso; sasinye isitya sokutshiza sesilivere, esiziishekele ezimashumi asixhenxe ngokweshekele yengcwele, zozibini zizele ngumgubo ocoliweyo womnikelo wokudla, ugalelwe ioli;",
